tem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mbf1665702767040.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mbf1665702767040.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mbf1665702767040.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mbf1665702767040\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                       \n filter\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__filter_66296\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Disable or enable debugging in a trigger.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__topic_d19331e1_d19332e1_d19333e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__p_d19334e1_d19335e1_d19336e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">filter</code> { <var class=\"keyword varname\">Trigger</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__topic_d13902e1_d13903e1_d13904e1_d13905e1_d13906e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d161770e68\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__li_d9506e1_d9507e1_d9508e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Trigger</var>—trigger abbreviation; causes all ProcScript statements in the trigger to be executed without pausing for debugging commands.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__li_d9509e1_d9510e1_d9511e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>—remove the filter and restore debugging in Trigger.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__li_d9512e1_d9513e1_d9514e1\">none—display the trigger currently being filtered. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__topic_d13907e1_d13908e1_d13909e1_d13910e1_d13911e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d161770e92\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__p_d19343e1_d19344e1_d19345e1\">While a filter is in effect, the debugger does not step through ProcScript instructions in the trigger or any ProcScript modules called from the trigger. Any breakpoints in the trigger are ignored. Only one filter can be active at a time.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__p_d19346e1_d19347e1_d19348e1\">By default there is a filter on the preDisplay trigger. This avoids the need to step through these triggers for items on the menu bar each time a component is first displayed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__section_f23_zjb_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d161770e104\">Example: </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">To disable the debugger while the read trigger is active:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mbf1665702767040__pre_u1z_zjb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">filter READ</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nzg1665702766049.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Debugging in Character Mode</a><p>On a client running in character mode, the debug ProcScript statement causes a Debug command line to be displayed at the bottom of the screen.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "filter Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 filter Disable or enable debugging in a trigger. filter { Trigger | off } Arguments Trigger —trigger abbreviation; causes all ProcScript statements in the trigger to be executed without pausing for debugging commands. off —remove the filter and restore debugging in Trigger. none—display the trigger currently being filtered. Description While a filter is in effect, the debugger does not step through ProcScript instructions in the trigger or any ProcScript modules called from the trigger. Any breakpoints in the trigger are ignored. Only one filter can be active at a time. By default there is a filter on the preDisplay trigger. This avoids the need to step through these triggers for items on the menu bar each time a component is first displayed. Example: To disable the debugger while the read trigger is active: filter READ Copy Related Links Debugging in Character Mode On a client running in character mode, the debug ProcScript statement causes a Debug command line to be displayed at the bottom of the screen. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}